### Get All Posts (Default - Published Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts

### Get All Posts (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts?skip=0&take=10&publishedOnly=true

### Get All Posts (Include Drafts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts?skip=0&take=20&publishedOnly=false

### Get All Posts (Second Page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts?skip=20&take=10&publishedOnly=true 